on, we recognized an aggregate loss of", "bbox": [194.9, 854.3, 1103.8, 879.3]}, {"text": "$100 in interest expense, net. The loss represented the difference between the net carrying amount and the", "bbox": [194.9, 879.3, 1103.7, 900.1]}, {"text": "total purchase price of the redeemed notes.", "bbox": [194.9, 904.3, 552.7, 925.2]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [153.2, 929.3, 177.5, 950.2]}, {"text": "In 2016, URNA issued $750 principal amount of 5 7/8 percent Senior Notes due 2026 and $750 principal", "bbox": [194.9, 929.3, 1103.6, 954.3]}, {"text": "amount of 5 1/2 percent Senior Notes due 2027. See below for additional detail.", "bbox": [194.9, 954.3, 854.8, 979.3]}, {"text": "Short-term debt", "bbox": [153.2, 1016.6, 288.3, 1037.5]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2016, our short-term debt primarily reflects $568 of borrowings under our accounts", "bbox": [194.9, 1054.4, 1103.7, 1075.2]}, {"text": "receivable securitization facility. As discussed below, in 2016, we amended and extended our accounts receivable", "bbox": [153.2, 1079.4, 1103.6, 1100.2]}, {"text": "securitization facility. During the year ended December 31, 2016, the monthly average amount outstanding under", "bbox": [153.2, 1104.4, 1103.7, 1125.2]}, {"text": "the accounts receivable securitization facility was $551 and the weighted-average interest rate thereon was", "bbox": [153.2, 1129.4, 1103.8, 1150.3]}, {"text": "1.2 percent. The maximum month-end amount outstanding under the accounts receivable securitization facility", "bbox": [153.2, 1154.4, 1103.6, 1175.3]}, {"text": "during the year ended December 31, 2016 was $621.", "bbox": [153.2, 1179.4, 593.6, 1200.3]}, {"text": "74", "bbox": [618.1, 1475.4, 638.9, 1496.2]}]}